{"tid":1373904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 到底可以點做令到政府肯正面回應我地訴求","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:00:44.000Z","uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78bcd68c1d4975e110bfe022b33fef078a2da433","tid":1373904,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"由69去到今日都差唔多兩個月時間<br />\n好肯定政府係心知肚明大家訴求<br />\n但到底仲有咩方法可以迫佢正面回應？<br />\n<br />\n每次示威遊行到最後就同啲警察鬥爭<br />\n但我地要鬥爭既對象係政府<br />\n班警察未夠班呀 加無呢個資格<br />\n我地要既係政府回應我地<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n專注五大訴求<br />\n1. 撤回修訂逃犯條例<br />\n2. 收回612暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 徹底調查及追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 立即落實雙真普選"},{"pid":"0528a60a63ba183e84dd08e9a8c0f7a24e9f14d9","tid":1373904,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"求賜教"},{"pid":"1fd82af799d3f6f5c549538c0c7e6497ea12319e","tid":1373904,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"求賜教"},{"pid":"9b079587f588a0c76db1d7940cb0a2ed8a5a9db8","tid":1373904,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"求賜教"},{"pid":"9025f27b0fbdbe4a038e1a101ef222a87b9b5842","tid":1373904,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"求賜教"},{"pid":"b86bba3a4c157a7e023bfa81ed2f1b01ef4fa61c","tid":1373904,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8f7f9463601ff8ec8a2cf4ec47605ae5f3e3e0","tid":1373904,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"冇 一齊戰到佢攰"}]}